outputs.output_descr:
The main objective of the project is to lay the groundwork for a sustainable Serbian/minority-language TV channel, which will:
- provide the minority communities in Kosovo with access to quality broadcast media and local news of relevance for their lives;
- foster reliable and unbiased journalism and thereby contributing to a better understanding and a more sustainable relationship between all communities and particularly between the Kosovo Albanian and Serbian communities;
- offer an attractive alternative to programmes broadcasted from Serbia proper and thereby contributing to the integration of the Kosovo Serb community.
